---
source: crates/duckpond/tests/parse_spec.rs
expression: spec
---
SPEC: Authentication
  SUMMARY: Allows users to sign in with email and password, manages their
    sessions, and provides logout.
  REQUIREMENT: Email-password login
    The system SHALL allow a registered user to authenticate using their
      email address and password.
    MARKS: test: code
    SCENARIO: Valid credentials
      WHENS:
        the user submits correct credentials
      THENS:
        the system issues a session token
    SCENARIO: Invalid password
      WHENS:
        the user submits an incorrect password
      THENS:
        the system rejects the login with a generic error
  REQUIREMENT: Session expiration
    The system SHALL expire idle sessions after 30 minutes.
    MARKS: test: code
    SCENARIO: Idle timeout
      GIVENS:
        an authenticated user
      WHENS:
        30 minutes pass with no requests
      THENS:
        the next request returns 401
  REQUIREMENT: Logout
    The system SHALL allow users to explicitly invalidate their session.
    MARKS: test: code
    SCENARIO: Explicit logout
      WHENS:
        the user submits a logout request
      THENS:
        the session token is invalidated
        future requests with that token are rejected
